rComments: One of my favourite history profs ever. He is so kind, sociable, intelligent, really encourages class participation & gives engaging lectures. He also provides information-dense slides which are very helpful. He's also very accessible outside of class hours for any questions or concerns you may have. Gives great feedback and sets clear expectations
Loved this class! This prof is a fair grader, he's truly passionate about First Nations and makes it exciting to go to class. My favourite class so far.
